      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TREMENDOUS SENSATION NZ (6) should be at peak fitness after three starts off a let-up. Has placed in two those, coming from this barrier for third last week. Her strike rate at this circuit and distance stands at 50 per cent and she could be ready to return to winning form. PLATINUM JEWEL (8) beat Tremendous Sensation with a 1.7m win last week, her third success from her last five outings at this circuit and distance. Goes back to the second line tonight but should enjoy a nice trail. ZAHRA LOU (1) won from this barrier last start and races well when third-up so could go on with it. IMA QUEEN BEE (9) has trialled since she was pulled up with cardiac arrythmia last time. May need luck from this draw but was a winner at this circuit and distance two back. BEAT SWEET (4) should be improved by last week's fourth, her first outing off a lengthy spell.",
